## 📂 Folder Structure
* `Arrays/` - Sorting, Searching, Two Pointers.
* `Sliding-Window/` - Fixed and Variable window problems.
* `Trees/` - BFS, DFS, and Binary Search Trees.
* `AI-Integration/` - Notes on how I'm using these algorithms in my Gym Form Fixer project.

## 🛠️ How to Run
All solutions are written in C++20. Use a standard compiler like `g++`:
`g++ problem_name.cpp -o output && ./output`
